content: I am not able to upload links from Reach into Threads. Is there a solution for this?
Hi Sharon, I could not find any solutions for you online but am tagging someone who might know. <@&1252689433208291358>

Sometimes Reach doesn't work perfectly with every social network. For example, it will take me to BlueSky but the image won't populate. In cases like that I simply upload the image from my phone to the social network (do a workaround). That may be the case with Threads. Thanks for your help sharing this important content with your connections. We appreciate it!
I thought you had fixed it. It started working with Threads last night.  Just in time for the debate. <:blueheart:1252803082849488956>
